  "title": "Executive, Nursing Admin (Nursing Home)- Up to $3.5K #HKH",
  "description": "<ul><li>Provide secretariat support to meetings related to the nursing department and RCD level committee(s). The Secretariatrole includes but is not limited to:</li><li>Scheduling of meetings</li><li>Creation and sending of invitations for meeting and monitoring of responses</li><li>Agenda setting with Nursing leaders and slides preparation if required</li><li>Logistics set up</li><li>Attendance taking</li><li>Minutes writing or notes taking when required</li><li>Tracking of action plans, if required</li><li>Support policy reviewsi. Track and maintain accurate records for reporting to Clinical Governance Committee, when required</li><li>Keep accurate and up-to-date records required for regulatory and organisational compliance and audit(s)</li><li>Assist Nurse Managers in managing dormitory list and any other databases, including but not limited to formatting and printing of materials</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements </strong></p><ul><li>Min N / O level </li><li>Min 2 years of experience in healthcare administration</li></ul><p><strong>Salary range: Up to $3.5K </strong><br /><strong>Office hours </strong><br /><strong>Nursing Home</strong><br /><br />Interested candidates, please forward your resume to kevynhuang@recruitexpress.com.sg </p><p>Consultant: Huang Jingsheng Kevyn (R1333338) <br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd (99C4599) </p>",
